<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 10:59:17 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>自行车通勤</title><link>https://some.pics/6a58b981666de</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🚲 通勤&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🚲 Commute" height="4012" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a58b981666de.jpg" width="3004"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 10:59:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a589fcfd4785</link><description>&lt;p&gt;卢浮宫-朗斯&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Louvre-Lens" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/6a589fcfd4785.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 09:09:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>雨夜独享台球时光</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5892ed95cc6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;昨晚我们顺道去了Society Garden，那是家靠近我们家的舒适户外啤酒花园酒吧。因为下雨，人流稀少，所以我们在游戏室打了几小时台球。平时这里拥挤很多，能几乎独享整个地方感觉真好。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A quiet outdoor bar at twilight, with colorful string lights and warm Edison bulbs glowing above the serving counters. The nearly empty beer garden has a relaxed, inviting atmosphere, with trees silhouetted against the deep blue evening sky." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a5892ed95cc6.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 08:14:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a587324e63e9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;继续练习HTML/CSS，这次制作一个带右侧边栏的布局。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bare-bones webpage with a header, main content area, sidebar with an author bio, and a footer" height="1688" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spencerdub/6a587324e63e9.png" width="2552"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spencerdub.some.pics"&gt;@spencerdub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:59:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>单列页面布局练习</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5872d2a3e7a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;HTML和CSS练习：制作一列页面布局&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Plain HTML page displaying placeholder text in a one-column layout" height="1430" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/spencerdub/6a5872d2a3e7a.png" width="1542"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://spencerdub.some.pics"&gt;@spencerdub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 05:57:41 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>